    "en": {
      "title": "Kerala Ganja worth 9 million in Navy custody",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In a special operation carried out by the Navy yesterday (18th) to chase away the Indian fishing vessels that carried out illegal fishing activities in the territorial waters belonging to Sri Lanka, the navy seized a stock of 30 kg (wet weight) of Kerala ganja floating in the sea near Kachchathivu Island. Worked out.",
        "In this special operation carried out yesterday (18th), 09 parcels floating near the island of Kachchativ were deployed to expel the Indian fishing boats that had illegally entered the territorial waters of the country by deploying the P412 fast fighter belonging to the fourth fast attack squadron attached to the Northern Naval Command. An amount of about 30 kg (wet weight) of Kerala ganja was taken into custody by the Navy.",
        "It is suspected that the smugglers may have abandoned this Kerala ganja without being able to bring it to the land due to the naval operations, and the gross street value of this stock of Kerala ganja is believed to be around 9 million rupees.",
        "Further, the Kerala Ganja stock seized by the Navy has been kept in the Navy's custody pending further legal proceedings."
      ],
